on jobs remain consistent across both snapshots. I'm getting confused about the timing here—the direct session actually ended at 04:44 based on the previous cycle's note, but the heartbeat state shows it was still active at that time. Let me trace through the sequence: the heartbeat ran at 04:44 and logged the state showing the direct session as active, but when I checked the sessions list earlier, it showed ended at 04:44 with a 24-second runtime, which means it must have completed right at that moment.\\n\\nNow looking at what's actually changed: the direct session has ended (it's gone from active to completed), the main session has disappeared entirely, and the group session has moved from idle to running. That's three notable changes, though none of them are critical failures—they're more like natural lifecycle transitions.\\n\\nActually, I need to reconsider what the cron job instructions are asking for. The directive says to stay silent if nothing has changed, but the threshold for \\\"changed\\\" isn't clearly defined. Should I treat these state transitions as significant enough to warrant a report, or are these normal operational changes that don't require notification?\\n\\nLooking at what's actually shifted: the Telegram session completed, the main session disappeared, and the group session started running. These feel like routine lifecycle events rather than actual failures or blockers. The pipeline itself remains healthy with no agents down and no blockers appearing. So strictly speaking, the core operational state hasn't changed—it's just session management happening as expected.\\n\\nBut the user did ask me to report whenever something changes, even if it's just a session dying. So I'll send a concise update acknowledging these transitions and confirming the pipeline is still operational.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_di3vmqukah8r_1\",\n              \"name\": \"write\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json\",\n                \"content\": \"{\\n  \\\"updatedAt\\\": \\\"2026-04-15T04:47:00Z\\\",\\n  \\\"activeSessions\\\": [\\n    \\\"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\\\",\\n    \\\"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\\\",\\n    \\\"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"idleSessions\\\": [],\\n  \\\"completedSinceLast\\\": [\\n    \\\"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\\\",\\n    \\\"agent:master-orchestrator:main\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"disappearedSessions\\\": [\\n    \\\"agent:master-orchestrator:main\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"failedSessions\\\": [],\\n  \\\"orphanedCrons\\\": [\\n    \\\"cron:ac986a8d-2425-40c7-835b-ed9b101b0bff\\\",\\n    \\\"cron:b653a6c0-143b-4b53-a242-034bc5fd9fca\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"lastReportSent\\\": \\\"2026-04-15T04:47:00Z\\\",\\n  \\\"lastReportGroup\\\": \\\"-5163901258\\\",\\n  \\\"degradedReason\\\": null,\\n  \\\"notes\\\": \\\"Lead direct session completed normally. Main session heartbeat ended. Group session activated. Pipeline HEALTHY.\\\"\\n}\\n\"\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 427,\n            \"output\": 1295,\n            \"totalTokens\": 22632,\n            \"cacheRead\": 14272,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 6638,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776228443941,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e4b5c8e21f4c78f54d825d18608eb\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"5cd7647f\",\n            \"seq\": 7\n          }\n        },\n        {\n        