 {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Đúng rồi Lead! Sau khi chạy xong thành công:\\n\\n- ✅ Config đã nằm ở `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\\n- ✅ Skills đã giải mã vào `~/.openclaw/workspaces/{agent}/skills/{agent}/SKILL.md`\\n- ✅ `skills.pack` đã unpack xong\\n\\n**Xóa thoải mái** — repo setup không còn cần nữa.\\n\\nChỉ giữ lại nếu muốn **chạy lại setup** (ví dụ: đổi team, reset config).\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 184,\n            \"output\": 280,\n            \"totalTokens\": 141970,\n            \"cacheRead\": 141261,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 245,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776228159398,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e4a426b9fceb5f975bd3327467063\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"79c4b6a7\",\n            \"seq\": 1729\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"ở repo tôi thấy có toàn bô folder như này .presence\\nfeat(ecosystem): add agent presence system — live status board for al…\\n3 days ago\\nagile-product-owner\\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\\n3 days ago\\nahv-openclaw-setup\\nfix: update clone URL to actual repo\\n1 minute ago\\nai-seo\\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\\n3 days ago\\nclean-code\\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\\n3 days ago\\ncode-reviewer\\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\\n3 days ago\\ncoding-standards\\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\\n3 days ago\\ncontent-strategy\\nfeat(