ions":["agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8bffa95f-1686-4571-a0ed-e69d265eb964"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:6053576134","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Lead is asking if after cloning, installing, and running the setup, they can delete the entire setup folder. The answer is: mostly yes, but they should keep the skills.pack if they want to re-run setup, and they should keep the bin/ahv-setup.js if they want to re-run. But actually, after setup completes, everything is installed into ~/.openclaw/ and the setup repo is no longer needed. The user can delete the repo folder after setup.\n\nHowever, the skills.pack gets unpacked into ~/.openclaw/ so after setup runs, the skills are already in place.\n\nSo yes, Lead can delete the setup folder after setup completes successfully."},{"type":"text","text":"Đúng rồi Lead! Sau khi chạy xong thành công:\n\n- ✅ Config đã nằm ở `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- ✅ Skills đã giải mã vào `~/.openclaw/workspaces/{agent}/skills/{agent}/SKILL.md`\n- ✅ `skills.pack` đã unpack xong\n\n**Xóa thoải mái** — repo setup không còn cần nữa.\n\nChỉ giữ lại nếu muốn **chạy lại setup** (ví dụ: đổi team, reset config)."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":184,"output":280,"totalTokens":141970,"cacheRead":141261,"cacheWrite":245,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776228159398,"responseId":"062e4a426b9fceb5f975bd3327467063","__openclaw":{"id":"79c4b6a7","seq":1729}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ở repo tôi thấy có toàn bô folder như này .presence\nfeat(ecosystem): add agent presence system — live status board for al…\n3 days ago\nagile-product-owner\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\nahv-openclaw-setup\nfix: update clone URL to actual repo\n1 minute ago\nai-seo\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\nclean-code\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\ncode-reviewer\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\ncoding-standards\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\ncontent-strategy\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\ndatabase-reviewer\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\ndatabase-schema-designer\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\nepic-design\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\nharness-optimizer\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\nmarket-intelligence\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\nmaster-orchestrator\nfix(git-workflow): update master-orchestrator DEV_GATE with new rules\n2 days ago\nops-manager\nfix(ecosystem): complete ops-manager workspace + add docs/memory to a…\n3 days ago\nperformance-optimizer\nfeat(ecosystem): add SKILL_GATES.md to all 34 agents — skill activati…\n3 days ago\nplanner\nfeat( khi clone về thì npm install sẽ load các skill này vào à hay các skill này đang bị đẩy nhầm lên"}],"timestamp":1776228252091,"__openclaw":{"id":"a842c3b2","seq":1730},"senderLabel":"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)"},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead is confused - they're seeing all the workspaces (34 agent folders) in the GitHub repo instead of just the `ahv-openclaw-setup` folder. \n\nThis is because the GitHub repo `maiychrus25/setup-openclaw` actually contains the entire `v4-ecosystem-review` workspace, not just the `ahv-openclaw-setup` folder. The remote was set to push the whole `v4-ecosystem-review` directory, not just the `ahv-openclaw-setup` subdirectory.\n\nWait, no - I pushed from the `v4-ecosystem-review` directory, which contains ALL the agent workspaces. The remote `origin` was set to `git@github.com:maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git`, so ALL of `v4-ecosystem-review` was pushed there.\n\n\nThat's exactly what happened - I pushed the entire `v4-ecosystem-review` directory to GitHub, so Lead is seeing all 34 agent workspaces instead of just the setup folder they needed. The setup-openclaw repo was just a subdirectory within that, not the whole thing."},{"type":"text","text":"Dạ **bị đẩy nhầm toàn bộ workspace lên** — vì em push từ thư mục cha `v4-ecosystem-review/`, không phải chỉ `ahv-openclaw-setup/`.\n\nTrên GitHub giờ chứa **34 workspaces + toàn bộ agent files** — không đúng. Lead cần xóa repo GitHub và tạo lại đúng.\n\n**Cách xử lý:**\n\n1. **Xóa repo** `setup-openclaw` trên GitHub\n2. **Tạo repo mới** trên GitHub\n3. **Xóa remote sai** trên máy:\n```bash\ngit remote remove origin\n```\n4. **Clone lại đúng folder**:\n```bash\n# Trên máy Lead, clone repo mới về\ngit clone https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git\ncd setup-openclaw\nnpm install\nnode bin/ahv-setup.js\n```\n\nTrên máy này (atu-ahv-ai006), repo đúng đã có sẵn tại:\n```\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/\n```\n\nLead muốn em xử lý xóa repo trên GitLab/GitHub không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":611,"output":532,"totalTokens":143008,"cacheRead":141433,"cacheWrite":