rtially done\n- The `ahv-openclaw-setup` package looks like the actual migration script\n\nI should clarify with the user what specific migration plan they're referring to, since the v4 infrastructure itself is complete."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5db3uvt21i7b_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review && git log origin/main..HEAD --oneline | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":351,"output":278,"totalTokens":23493,"cacheRead":21721,"cacheWrite":1143,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776226544532,"responseId":"062e43f1811a478cf13f9fe7f0c373a5","__openclaw":{"id":"02da540b","seq":10}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a full picture. Let me summarize for the Lead:\n\n**V4 Ecosystem Migration - Status:**\n\n✅ **Infrastructure (DONE):**\n- 34 agent workspaces created\n- Presence system (init/set/broadcast)\n- SKILL_GATES.md for all 34 agents\n- DEV_GATE.md for 5 key agents\n- HANDOVER.md / FEEDBACK.md templates\n- OPENSPEC_TRIGGER\n- Ecosystem backup (2026-04-11)\n- GIT_WORKFLOW.md (ecosystem standard)\n- 17 commits ahead of origin/main (NEED PUSH)\n\n⚠️ **Pending Cleanup:**\n\n\n- Project repos sitting in the v4-ecosystem-review workspace that should be relocated\n- ops-manager directory partially cleaned up with remaining deleted files\n- ahv-openclaw-setup package needs review for how it fits into the migration\n\nI should clarify with the Lead what they mean by \"plan migration\" — whether they're asking about the v4 infrastructure setup status or something else entirely."},{"type":"text","text":"## V4 Ecosystem Migration — Status\n\n**Tổng quan:**\n\n| Hạng mục | Trạng thái |\n|---|---|\n| 34 agent workspaces | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| Presence system | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| SKILL_GATES / DEV_GATE | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| HANDOVER / FEEDBACK templates | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| Ecosystem backup | ✅ (2026-04-11) |\n| GIT_WORKFLOW.md | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| **17 commits chưa push** | ⚠️ Cần push lên origin/main |\n\n**Chưa xong / Cần dọn dẹp:**\n- Project repos (`ahv-qlhv-be`, `ahv-qlhv-fe`, `ahv-dtlx-backend`) nằm trong workspace v4-ecosystem-review — không đúng chỗ\n- `ahv-openclaw-setup` — cần review xem có phải migration script chính thức không\n- ops-manager: đã xóa nhưng chưa commit cleanup\n\n**Cần Lead xác nhận:** \"Plan migration\" ở đây là migration gì?\n1. **V4 infrastructure** → ✅ gần xong, cần push 17 commits + dọn repo\n2. **Migration script (ahv-openclaw-setup)** → đọc nội dung rồi báo cáo\n3. **Khác** → nói rõ hơn\n\nChờ Lead hướng dẫn tiếp."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":477,"output":565,"totalTokens":24430,"cacheRead":22455,"cacheWrite":933,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776226552335,"responseId":"062e43f9b5eb94d8ca5013359b1987c9","__openclaw":{"id":"6d34c150","seq":12}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: Agent Status to Lead","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776226484570,"sessionId":"1809bef8-e85f-45f1-bec9-a828745f9877","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":34262,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776226484036,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/1809bef8-e85f-45f1-bec9-a828745f9877.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive view of all sessions. Let me analyze the active master-orchestrator sessions (excluding this cron session).\n\nCurrent time: 2026-04-15 04:14 UTC\n\nLet me identify the ACTIVE master-orchestrator sessions (status: running, excluding this cron session e7885813):\n\n1. **`agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d`** — QLHV 5p Monitor cron\n   - Status: running\n   - startedAt: 1776225348964\n   - Current time: ~1776226440 (from this cron run at 04:14)\n   - Duration: about 18 minutes since it spawned around 04:09 UTC with 3 active planner children still running, continuing the monitoring cycle from the 04:09 UTC report.\n\n2. **`agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef`** — DTLX 5p Monitor cron\n   - Status: running\n   - startedAt: 1776199558073\n   - This started much earlier (around 02:05 UTC based on the DTLX 5p report at 04:12), though the QLHV 5p Monitor was last updated at 04:09 UTC\n\n, it was running with 3 children\n   - Duration: ~2h+9m = about 129 minutes\n   - Child sessions: c2d275a5 (done), 63bb70ce (done), ba49ac6d (done) - these appear to be from earlier cycles\n   - Actually, the DTLX 5p cron started at 1776199558073 ms. Converting: that's about April 15, 02:05 UTC\n   - Current time: ~1776226440 ms = April 15, 04:14 UTC\n   - Duration: about 129 minutes (2h 9m)\n   - UpdatedAt: 1776226323464 (this is from a message at 04:12 UTC - so it's been running for 2+ hours)\n   - Still running\n\nNow looking at the third session, the QLHV Ecosystem group has been active for about 17 hours since April 14 around 11:20 UTC, with 4 child sessions including prompt-optimizer, senior-backend (multiple instances), and senior-frontend, though it ended normally back around 11:23 UTC.\n\nFor the fourth session with Lead direct, it's only been running for about 3 minutes since starting at 04:11 UTC, and has spawned 6 child subagents so far.\n\nNow looking at the remaining sessions: the main session ended quickly about 4.8 hours ago, and the DTLX Ecosystem group failed over an hour ago, so neither is active anymore.\n\nI need to reconsider what \"active\" actually means here—the question asks for all active master-orchestrator sessions, and while the original report mentioned 3 active sessions, I should clarify whether that refers to currently running sessions or includes recently active ones based on their last update time. I'm realizing the instruction is asking me to filter specifically for master-orchestrator sessions, not all agents—so I need to exclude subagents like the planner and senior-backend tasks and only include sessions from the `agent:master-orchestrator:*` prefix. Let me go through the session list and pull out only those matching that criteria. Looking at the remaining sessions, I see the main orchestrator session ended over 4 hours ago, so it's not active, and the QLHV ecosystem group session ended normally several hours back as well.\n\nNow I'm reviewing the other cron and agent sessions—the DTLX ecosystem group is marked as failed and ended an hour ago, the daily briefing cron never started properly, and there are a couple of orphaned cron sessions that are quite old and stuck.\n\nLooking at what's actually still running, I can see four active master-orchestrator sessions: the QLHV 5p monitor has been going for about 18 minutes with three planner subagents still working on it, the DTLX 5p monitor is running longer at around 129 minutes, and the QLHV ecosystem group has been active for about 17 hours. Looking at the Lead direct session more carefully, the child subagents from that 04:11 cycle are all done or failed, but there was a more recent interaction at 04:14 UTC where the parent session was actively editing a file in the ahv-setup.js project—this is fresh work happening right now, not a stale state.\n\nNow I'm calculating the actual duration for each active session by subtracting their start timestamps from the current time of 1776226440 milliseconds, which gives me the elapsed time in seconds for the QLHV 5p monitor and the other running processes.\n\nI need to verify that the DTLX 5p Monitor is actually still running by checking if it's actively working, rather than just being listed as a parent session with old children.\n\nLooking at the session timestamps, the QLHV 5p Monitor started at 04:09 UTC while the DTLX 5p Monitor started much earlier at 02:05 UTC, so they're separate sessions. I can confirm the DTLX 5p Monitor is running since it's in the list with that status. Now I should format and send this status report via Telegram to the Lead."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nvgkf39gobo2_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","message":"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 04:14 UTC 15 Apr\n\nActive sessions: 4\n• cron:ed2d0b5d (QLHV 5p Monitor): running — QLHV ecosystem monitoring cycle — ~18m\n• cron:6f3323ef (DTLX 5p Monitor): running — DTLX ecosystem monitoring cycle — ~129m\n• telegram:group:-5163901258 (QLHV Ecosystem): running — group task (4 children: prompt-optimizer, senior-backend×2, senior-frontend) — ~17h 29m\n• telegram:direct:6053576134 (Lead direct): running — working on ahv-setup.js path replacements — ~3m\n\nPipeline: DEGRADED ⚠️\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Blockers: ⚠️ DTLX group (-5168104492) failed (since 03:16 UTC) | ⚠️ cron:ac986a8d orphan (~34h) | ⚠️ cron:b653a6c0 orphan (~29h)\n\n— Orbis 🌐","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":28918,"output":1415,"totalTokens":44484,"cacheRead":13849,"cacheWrite":302,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776226499855,"responseId":"062e43c492a6db0d22a15455842bc3ef","__openclaw":{"id":"dfd6597f","seq":4}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1776226562383,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted.","__openclaw":{"id":"061524f4","seq":6}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Daily Briefing 